window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Shiver me timbers!</p> <p>The mysterious new leader of the Brightlings is after a secret weapon. The catch? It's hidden somewhere in Voltis, a forbidden place where violent elemental forces will slap you around like a redheaded stepchild. Naturally, Justin can't let that happen and convinces Elyssa, Shelton, and Adam to tag along, because who doesn't want to ride a flying ship into hurricane-force winds while lightning tries to rip you a new one?</p> <p>Based on a true story (it isn't), <i>Ominous Odyssey</i> is an inspiring story about why world domination is best left to the professionals.</p>"; 
